# Presence Detection Documentation

When modifying presence detection files, the documentation at `docs/PRESENCE.md` may need updates.

## Before Completing Changes

Review if your changes affect any of these documented areas:

| Area | What to Check |
|------|---------------|
| **Home Presence** | Device trackers, Person integration config, Bayesian sensors |
| **Room Presence** | ESPresense config, BLE base stations, room detection logic |
| **Zone Presence** | Zone definitions, zone-based automations |
| **Transition States** | Just Arrived, Just Left logic, timing thresholds |

## Key Patterns

- `*_presence.yaml` - Presence sensor definitions
- `*_room_presence.yaml` - Room-level BLE presence
- `*_person.yaml` - Person entity templates (may include presence attributes)

## Action Required

After making changes, ask the user:

> "I've modified presence detection. Should I review and update `docs/PRESENCE.md` to reflect these changes?"

If the user agrees, read the current documentation and update any sections affected by the changes.
